ll as torsion, sway, and anti-roll bars; locking, free wheel, and floater hubs, as well as hub parts and spindles; gear shifters/shift towers; hydraulic gear pumps; and differential housings, pinion and end yokes, pinion support, and shims/shim kits. It also provides lunch box and differential Posi lockers; nodular iron differential covers; full and mini spools; axle bearing pullers clam shell style products, carrier and pinion bearing pullers, axle bearing pullers plate style, and differential housing spreaders, as well as various forged and cast differential parts for 4-wheel drive and high-performance racing vehicles. In addition, the company offers engineering solutions, including conceptualization, development, validation, implementation, and manufacturing of products. It exports its products. The company was formerly known as Emmforce Inc. and changed its name to Emmforce Autotech Limited in October 2023. Emmforce Autotech Limited was founded in 1993 and is based in Solan, India."}}